OL,3,CTriple killer Valdo Calocane held
OL,4,Cflatmate in headlock, inquiry told
OL,6,FA flatmate of Valdo Calocane has told
OL,7,Fthe inquiry into the 2023 Nottingham
OL,8,Fattacks how the triple killer put him
OL,9,Fin a headlock and then prevented him
OL,10,Ffrom leaving their shared kitchen.
OL,12,FThe witness, identified at the inquiry
OL,13,Fonly as Christopher, described the
OL,14,Fincident in Nottingham in 2022 as
OL,15,F"distressing" and said a police
OL,16,Fofficer was later "dismissive" and did
OL,17,Fnot arrest Calocane.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
