OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772885578
OL,3,CTriple killer Valdo Calocane held
OL,4,Cflatmate in headlock, inquiry told
OL,6,FMobile phone footage of paranoid
OL,7,Fschizophrenic Calocane holding his
OL,8,Fflatmate in a headlock was shown to
OL,9,Fthe central London inquiry on
OL,10,FThursday, as Christopher gave evidence.
OL,12,FThe inquiry has previously heard how
OL,13,FCalocane, then a mechanical
OL,14,Fengineering student at the University
OL,15,Fof Nottingham, headbutted, punched and
OL,16,Fswung handcuffs at a police officer on
OL,17,FSeptember 3, 2021, causing swelling to
OL,18,Fhis face.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
