OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772885578
OL,3,CTriple killer Valdo Calocane held
OL,4,Cflatmate in headlock, inquiry told
OL,6,FThe killer went on to fatally stab
OL,7,FUniversity of Nottingham
OL,8,Fundergraduates Barnaby Webber and
OL,9,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar, both 19, and
OL,10,Fcaretaker Ian Coates, 65, and
OL,11,Fattempted to kill three more people in
OL,12,Fthe early hours of June 13 2023.
OL,14,FIn his evidence to the inquiry,
OL,15,FChristopher said he was attacked by
OL,16,FCalocane on January 15, 2022 in shared
OL,17,Fsix-room student accommodation in
OL,18,FFaraday Road, in Nottingham.
OL,20,F"I dodged the punch and then we were
OL,21,Fwrestling."
OL,26,@|D@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
