CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772885578
OL,3,CTriple killer Valdo Calocane held
OL,4,Cflatmate in headlock, inquiry told
OL,6,FThe witness said he and others would
OL,7,Fhear occasional noises from Calocane's
OL,8,Froom.
OL,10,F"He wasn't ever warm to us,"
OL,11,FChristopher said. "The bathroom had
OL,12,Fbeen left (by Calocane) in probably
OL,13,Fthe worst state that it had been up to
OL,14,Fthat point.
OL,16,F"I decided that I couldn't shower
OL,17,Fbecause of it.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@\O]sD@SOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772885578
OL,3,CTriple killer Valdo Calocane held
OL,4,Cflatmate in headlock, inquiry told
OL,6,F"I said (to Calocane) that this is not
OL,7,Ffair to other people. A few hours
OL,8,Flater he came into the kitchen so I
OL,9,Fsaid to him 'Have you cleaned it up
OL,10,Fyet?'
OL,12,F"He said 'No, I'm not going to'."
OL,14,FCalocane then came "flying across the
OL,15,Froom" and threw a punch, Christopher
OL,16,Fsaid, adding: "I dodged the punch and
OL,17,Fthen we were wrestling. He ended up
OL,18,Fgetting me in a headlock."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUtD@aO]vD@TOUwD@EO]xD@OOUzD@
OL,26,AZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
