PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772885578
OL,3,CTriple killer Valdo Calocane held
OL,4,Cflatmate in headlock, inquiry told
OL,6,FChristopher told the inquiry he then
OL,7,Fcalled the police, but Calocane would
OL,8,Fnot let him leave the flat and stared
OL,9,Fat him as he waited for officers to
OL,10,Farrive.
OL,12,F"I felt like it was dismissive"
OL,14,FAsked by counsel to the inquiry if
OL,15,Fwaiting for police with Calocane had
OL,16,Ffelt like a hostage situation,
OL,17,FChristopher, who decided not to press
OL,18,Fcharges, said: "It did feel like that
OL,19,Fat the time, because when the assault
OL,20,Fhappened there were two other people
OL,21,Fin the room.
OL,26,@tD@AOUzD@POU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772885578
OL,3,CTriple killer Valdo Calocane held
OL,4,Cflatmate in headlock, inquiry told
OL,6,F"It was just me and him at that point
OL,7,Fand he's staring into my eyes. Yeah,
OL,8,Fit did feel like that to me."
OL,10,FChristopher was left with a stiff and
OL,11,Fpainful neck and said that after
OL,12,Fspeaking to police who arrived at the
OL,13,Fscene he was told by an officer that
OL,14,Fthe incident was "going to be common
OL,15,Fassault".
OL,17,FHe told the inquiry: "I felt like it
OL,18,Fwas dismissive in a way. He (the
OL,19,Fofficer) said we can do this thing
OL,20,Fcalled restorative justice."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@]O]vD@ROUwD@HO]yD@VOU|D@\O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772885578
OL,3,CTriple killer Valdo Calocane held
OL,4,Cflatmate in headlock, inquiry told
OL,6,FAn officer went to speak to Calocane,
OL,7,Fthe witness said, but he did not agree
OL,8,Fto apologise and "they did not arrest
OL,9,Fhim and nothing happened".
OL,11,FChristopher added: "They asked me if I
OL,12,Fwanted to pursue it. At that point to
OL,13,Fbe honest I kind of thought it was a
OL,14,Fwaste of time. I just said 'leave it
OL,15,Fat that'.
OL,17,F"The only thing I wanted was for him
OL,18,Fto not live in the flat any more."
OL,20,F"I got lucky"
OL,26,@pD@ROUqD@YO]sD@TOUyD@AOUzD@bO]|D@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
