OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772885578
OL,3,CTriple killer Valdo Calocane held
OL,4,Cflatmate in headlock, inquiry told
OL,6,FAt the end of his evidence,
OL,7,FChristopher said he believed he and
OL,8,Fothers were put at risk because they
OL,9,Fwere not given background information
OL,10,Fabout Calocane's medical history.
OL,12,F"I got lucky and I'm fine," he said.
OL,14,F"Maybe I wouldn't have, but that's
OL,15,Fwhere we are."
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@[O]vD@AOUwD@NO]
