OL,3,CTriple killer Valdo Calocane held
OL,4,Cflatmate in headlock, inquiry told
OL,6,FThe inquiry heard on Wednesday how
OL,7,FCalocane was charged with assaulting
OL,8,Fan emergency worker and was summonsed
OL,9,Fto attend Nottingham Magistrates'
OL,10,FCourt in September 2022, but he failed
OL,11,Fto appear.
OL,13,FA warrant for his arrest was issued by
OL,14,Fthe court, but Calocane had not been
OL,15,Farrested by police before he committed
OL,16,Fthe attacks in June 2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
