OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772885578
OL,3,CTriple killer Valdo Calocane held
OL,4,Cflatmate in headlock, inquiry told
OL,6,FCalocane is currently detained
OL,7,Findefinitely in a high-security
OL,8,Fhospital after prosecutors accepted
OL,9,Fhis not guilty pleas to murder at his
OL,10,Fsentencing at Nottingham Crown Court
OL,11,Fin January 2024.
OL,13,FThe inquiry continues.
